OL,3,CWorld Cup fever builds in Cumbria as
OL,4,CEngland get set to take on Ghana
OL,6,FExcitement is building across Cumbria
OL,7,Fas England get set to take on Ghana in
OL,8,Ftheir second game of the 2026 World
OL,9,FCup.
OL,11,FChildren at Bishop Harvey Goodwin
OL,12,FSchool in Carlisle have been enjoying
OL,13,Fplenty of football alongside their
OL,14,Fstudies as hope for World Cup success
OL,15,Fgrips the nation.
OL,17,FThe Three Lions won their opening game
OL,18,Fagainst Croatia and take on Ghana on
OL,19,FTuesday evening in Boston.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/5
