OL,3,CWorld Cup fever builds in Cumbria as
OL,4,CEngland get set to take on Ghana
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV Border, Head Teacher
OL,7,Fat Bishop Harvey Goodwin, Kate
OL,8,FHolland, said: "Well the World Cup
OL,9,Ffever has been building and as you can
OL,10,Ftell the children are so excited.
OL,12,F"They are enjoying their football
OL,13,Feveryday and talking about what is
OL,14,Fgoing on in the World Cup. I am
OL,15,Fexpecting some very tired children in
OL,16,Fschool tomorrow."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/5
