OL,3,CWorld Cup fever builds in Cumbria as
OL,4,CEngland get set to take on Ghana
OL,6,FNathan Naylor is a football coach and
OL,7,Fprovides sessions to the kids during
OL,8,Fschool. He says that he notices a
OL,9,Fpositive upturn in interest when the
OL,10,Fnational side is performing well.
OL,12,FHe said: "eah especially when England
OL,13,Fare doing well, I think some of the
OL,14,Fbigger names and personalities are
OL,15,Fgood role models for the kids to look
OL,16,Fup to."
OL,18,FGhana will be looking to upset
OL,19,FEngland's party though and come into
OL,20,Fthe game also off the back of victory
OL,21,Fin their opening game against Panama.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/5
