OL,3,CWorld Cup fever builds in Cumbria as
OL,4,CEngland get set to take on Ghana
OL,6,FCharles Awuah is a Ghanian living in
OL,7,FCarlisle and has high hopes that he
OL,8,Fwill be the one celebrating on Tuesday
OL,9,Fevening.
OL,11,FHe said: "We won our first game so it
OL,12,Fhas given us that confidence and going
OL,13,Finto this game we know that England
OL,14,Fare very good.
OL,16,F"We are looking forward to it and we
OL,17,Fare prepared for the game and I know
OL,18,Fat least we will make it a good game
OL,19,Fand it will not be a walkover. We are
OL,20,Fprepared and ready to give England a
OL,21,Fgame and we are hoping to win."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/5
